title: PPPP M. Farooq Awan wins PS-95 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarians’ (PPPP) Muhammad Farooq Awan has won the Sindh Assembly election from PS-95, Korangi- Karachi-VI by securing 16,386 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Raja Azher Khan of , the Independent, who bagged votes 11,027.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 38.94 %.
